      "workout_summary": "3m @102W | 4\u00d710s @366W / 50s rec | 3m @152W | 2m @132W | 5m @183W | 3m @102W | 10\u00d740s @222W / 20s rec | 5m @102W | 10\u00d740s @222W / 20s rec | 5m @102W | 3m @254W | 5m @102W",
